9 COMMITTEE SUBSTITUTE
10 An Act relating to counties and county officers;
amending 19 O.S. 2021, Section 1501, as last amended
11 by Section 1, Chapter 85, O.S.L. 2025 (19 O.S. Supp.
2025, Section 1501), which relates to county
12 purchasing; permitting county purchasing agent to
solicit quotes; amending 19 O.S. 2021, Section 1505,
13 as last amended by Section 2, Chapter 85, O.S.L. 2025
(19 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 1505), which relates to
14 procedures for the operation of county government;
removing language for clarity; repealing 19 O.S.
15 2021, Section 1801, which relates to reverse auction
bidding; and providing an effective date.
16
17
18 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
